Hello everyone! I've created a chatbot on Telegram to connect people anonymously.I've posted on /r/SGExams so I'm not sure if you've seen it  but here's the postThis is the bot@TeletextSGBot. Basically  it's just a chat bot for you to select your interests  and match with people with the similar interests. Hopefully this can be a platform for students to make friends  or get listening ears to help them cope and handle with the stress of daily life. Would be great if any of you have time this weekend to give it a try and let me know how it is  and hopefully you can have some fun conversations and new friends along the way.Please help me to upvote on Reddit so it gains some visibility too! A bigger userbase makes it a better experience for all that are using it.
